2017-06-27 22:44:39 - database error:  AbanteCart core v.1.2.9 SQL Error: You have an error in your SQL syntax; check the manual that corresponds to your MySQL server version for the right syntax to use near '-1605842274,20' at line 38<br />Error No: 1064<br />SQL: SELECT *,
						p.product_id,
						COALESCE(  ( SELECT p2sp.price
					FROM abc_product_specials p2sp
					WHERE p2sp.product_id = p.product_id
							AND p2sp.customer_group_id = '1'
							AND ((p2sp.date_start = '0000-00-00' OR p2sp.date_start < NOW())
							AND (p2sp.date_end = '0000-00-00' OR p2sp.date_end > NOW()))
					ORDER BY p2sp.priority ASC, p2sp.price ASC LIMIT 1
				 ) , p.price) as final_price,
						pd.name AS name, 
						pd.blurb,
						m.name AS manufacturer,
						ss.name AS stock,
						 ( SELECT AVG(r.rating)
						 FROM abc_reviews r
						 WHERE p.product_id = r.product_id AND status = 1
						 GROUP BY r.product_id 
				 ) AS rating ,
						 ( SELECT COUNT(rw.review_id)
						 FROM abc_reviews rw
						 WHERE p.product_id = rw.product_id AND status = 1
						 GROUP BY rw.product_id
				 ) AS review 
		FROM abc_products p
				LEFT JOIN abc_product_descriptions pd
					ON (p.product_id = pd.product_id
							AND pd.language_id = '1')
				LEFT JOIN abc_products_to_stores p2s ON (p.product_id = p2s.product_id)
				LEFT JOIN abc_manufacturers m ON (p.manufacturer_id = m.manufacturer_id)
				LEFT JOIN abc_stock_statuses ss
						ON (p.stock_status_id = ss.stock_status_id
								AND ss.language_id = '1')
		LEFT JOIN abc_products_to_categories p2c
			ON (p.product_id = p2c.product_id)

					WHERE p2sp.product_id = p.product_id
							AND p2sp.customer_group_id = '1'
							AND ((p2sp.date_start = '0000-00-00' OR p2sp.date_start < NOW())
							AND (p2sp.date_end = '0000-00-00' OR p2sp.date_end > NOW()))
					ORDER BY p2sp.priority ASC, p2sp.price ASC LIMIT 1
				 ) , p.price) as final_price,
						pd.name AS name, 
						pd.blurb,
						m.name AS manufacturer,
						ss.name AS stock,
						 ( SELECT AVG(r.rating)
						 FROM abc_reviews r
						 WHERE p.product_id = r.product_id AND status = 1
						 GROUP BY r.product_id 
				 ) AS rating ,
						 ( SELECT COUNT(rw.review_id)
						 FROM abc_reviews rw
						 WHERE p.product_id = rw.product_id AND status = 1
						 GROUP BY rw.product_id
				 ) AS review 
		FROM abc_products p
				LEFT JOIN abc_product_descriptions pd
					ON (p.product_id = pd.product_id
							AND pd.language_id = '1')
				LEFT JOIN abc_products_to_stores p2s ON (p.product_id = p2s.product_id)
				LEFT JOIN abc_manufacturers m ON (p.manufacturer_id = m.manufacturer_id)
				LEFT JOIN abc_stock_statuses ss
						ON (p.stock_status_id = ss.stock_status_id
								AND ss.language_id = '1')
		LEFT JOIN abc_products_to_categories p2c
			ON (p.product_id = p2c.product_id)
